{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "lyceon-api",
		"name": "Lyceon - APIs",
		"description": "Complete API collection for testing mounted endpoints locally.\n\nSee docs/route-registry.md and docs/entitlements-map.md for the canonical source of truth.\n\n## Quick Start\n1. Sign in via `POST /api/auth/signin` — cookies are set automatically.\n2. All subsequent requests use the stored cookies for auth.\n3. Update collection variables (studentId, sessionId, etc.) as needed.",
